This project use the API from https://www.themoviedb.org
You will need to request an API Key from moviedb to run that code.

To run the code create the following xml file
/MyAndroidStudioProjectPath/PopularMovies/app/src/main/res/values/api_key.xml

With the following content
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<resources>
    <string name="api_key">MyApiKeyfromTheMovieDB</string>
</resources>

